snippet.title: Vertical Angles - MathHelp.com - Geometry Help
snippet.description: For a complete lesson on vertical angles, go to http://www.MathHelp.com - 1000+ online math lessons featuring a personal math teacher inside every lesson! In this lesson, students learn the definition of vertical angles and the vertical angle theorem, and are asked to find the measures of vertical angles using Algebra. Students also solve two-column proofs involving vertical angles.
